{"tid":1741371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[11月24前要一路見到呢個post]幫到義士鄭錦滿嘅辦法只得一個！！！","createTime":"2019-11-20T10:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:59:17.000Z","uid":163207,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55dec79f7f79df2c462d964430c25431834ac3ed","tid":1741371,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QmMH0je.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmMH0je.jpg&h=5d974d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【2019年區議會選舉 請支持熱血公民：在亂世相信自己，為社區做好選擇】<br />\n<br />\n經過連月的反逃犯修例示威，普遍市民認為今年的區議會選舉會與過去的有所不同。<br />\n<br />\n有的人認為大部分群眾已經「覺醒」，有的人預期民主派大勝，有的人更奢言議會變天；然而沒有制度變革，我們始終未能從根本保障人權，香港亦難求長治久安。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2016年立法會選舉，全民制憲永續基本法運動失敗後，我們早已預計今後的紛亂日子，</strong></span>自14年雨傘革命、16年DQ事件，以至近月的逃犯爭議，政府一貫專橫施政，官迫民反乃自然之理，世道怎會不亂？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>熱血公民一直面對來自四方八面的打壓、刻意排斥、惡意中傷；面對無窮無盡的抹黑</strong></span>，我們仍然深信做好自己，做事不苟不懈，克勤小物，終會得到越來越多同道、有識之士的賞識及支持。<br />\n<br />\n鼓動人心的口號是可以短暫的激勵士氣；唯「理念」讓我們團結地堅持下去，直至香港復興的那天。<br />\n<br />\n感謝廣大的支持者，以及一眾同道一直以來的支持，今屆區議會選舉我們投身其中，是為了實在地把理念植根社區，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請支持我們五位熱血公民區選候選人</strong></span>。"},{"pid":"08e65320410ac461f5604c6d12d08a23189e92bc","tid":1741371,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cffae404308a75160e14affef9feb98e4c6a7a0","tid":1741371,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"4ec82c6e0f27bd893aa4d31cfd01ed44fcbdf5c5","tid":1741371,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cffae404308a75160e14affef9feb98e4c6a7a0","tid":1741371,"uid":145296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"販民有無人做義士呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653d2bf4356cccf416911a6156302cde498a258b","tid":1741371,"uid":3696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"青熱城話去poly 果啲on9仔黎喎，話應該要岀黎自首喎。<br />\n話累左咁多手足喎，佢做乜唔聽國師話去自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有無內疚會唔會岀黎道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59a8b1719ef5a38b789f3c9fbc6150f64735d61","tid":1741371,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一票不投熱青城</span></span>"},{"pid":"c320686a915655aedb25e605a14f3076b5df3573","tid":1741371,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"653d2bf4356cccf416911a6156302cde498a258b","tid":1741371,"uid":3696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"青熱城話去poly 果啲on9仔黎喎，話應該要岀黎自首喎。<br />\n話累左咁多手足喎，佢做乜唔聽國師話去自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢有無內疚會唔會岀黎道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔好講住先"},{"pid":"98a4b9328573fb21e0e99de4a23732c270332df1","tid":1741371,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e59a8b1719ef5a38b789f3c9fbc6150f64735d61","tid":1741371,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一票不投熱青城</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd343c265f22f7a4598e6d056df15396c5ffca17","tid":1741371,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"再次發動圖書館戰爭"}]}